ygData.msgSnippet: Tesch Val D Nmark or something very similar is the actual name :-). He is very easy to get to since nothing in Paw can see invis that I have noticed.  I
ygData.messageBody:
Tesch Val D'Nmark or something very similar is the actual name :-).
He is very easy to get to since nothing in Paw can see invis that I
have noticed. I waltzed right into his room with my group, saw him
holding a sword, and we commenced to taking him out. Not sure about
the old room names, but he is found ...
.
.
..
.
.
.
.
In the room to the left, behind the Judges/Executioners, then take
the right door.
